   "source": [
    "for n in ['test_linear_data.txt', 'test_quad_data.txt']:\n",
    "    data = np.loadtxt(n)\n",
    "    xdata = data[:,0]\n",
    "    xerr = data[:,2]\n",
    "    ydata = data[:,1]\n",
    "    yerr = data[:,3]\n",
    "    x = unp.uarray(xdata,xerr)\n",
    "    y = unp.uarray(ydata,yerr)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "    ff = plot.auto(xdata, ydata, fmt='.', label='data', xaxis=\"x in a.u.\",yaxis=\"y in a.u.\",sigmas=1)"
   ]
